<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h1>
      Make or Break!
    </h1>

    <p>We've all been there. You made a plan weeks in advance, but the day comes by. You're too tired to follow through, or you simply don't want to go. After you make a plan, you can choose to break it. But the plan will only truly be broken if everyone clicks on "BREAK!". Otherwise, you'll rally and go through with it. Have fun! Make the plan or break the plan.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
    <h2>
      Make a new plan
    </h2>

    <form action="/insert_plan" method="post">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="recipient_id_box">
          Who do you want to make it with?
        </label>

        <input type="text" id="recipient_id_box" name="query_recipient_id" class="form-control">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="plan_time_box">
          When is this plan?
        </label>

        <input type="datetime-local" id="plan_time_box" name="query_plan_time" class="form-control">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="location_box">
          Where is the plan?
        </label>

        <input type="text" id="location_box" name="query_location" class="form-control">
      </div>

      <button class="btn btn-block btn-outline-secondary">
        Make Plan
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
<h2>Your Plans</h2>
<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <table class="table">
      <tr>

        <th>
          Recipient
        </th>

        <th>
          Status
        </th>

        <th>
          Plan time
        </th>

        <th>
          Location
        </th>

        <th>
          Created at
        </th>

        <th>
          Updated at
        </th>

        <th>
        </th>
      </tr>

      <% @plans.each do |plan| %>
      <tr>

        <td>
          <%= plan.recipient_id %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= plan.status %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= plan.plan_time %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= plan.location %>
        </td>

        <td>
          <%= time_ago_in_words(plan.created_at) %> ago
        </td>
        <td>
          <%= time_ago_in_words(plan.updated_at) %> ago
        </td>

        <td>
          <a href="/plans/<%= plan.id %>">
            Show details
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
